# Requisitioning a Global Resource

Requisition requests will remain publically visible at all times. Any OSG member may request any number of resources, any other OSG members may pledge resources to the request.

## How to Requisition a Global Resource

Create a new document in the Global-Resource repository using this naming convention: "Requisition Request - [Time/Skill/Object] [DDMMYY HHMM] [Your-OSG-Name].md" 

##Examples Filenames:

Requisition Request - Global - Legal Skill - 070617 1257 Green-Skye-Road.md  
Requisition Request - Global - 4 Hours - 171217 0307 Red-Hill-Mountain.md  
Requisition Request - Global - Web Server - 171217 0307 Eight-Block-Store.md  


